title: Kelsie Schelling /// Part 2 /// 84
description:
Kelsie Schelling//////84

TrueCrimeGarage.com

Kelsie Schelling was 21 years old and 8 weeks pregnant when she vanished on February 4, 2013. She had the first doctor's visit of her pregnancy earlier that day. After the trip to the doctor and a shift at work, Kelsie drove two hours to Pueblo, Colorado to visit her boyfriend and father of her child, Donthe Lucas. What happened once Kelsie got to Pueblo remains a mystery. She hasn't been seen since. Kelsie Schelling is 26 years old. She is 5 foot 3 inches tall, 120 pounds, and she is white with brown hair and hazel eyes. She was last seen on February 4, 2013 in the area of Manor Ridge Drive and Siena Drive in Pueblo Colorado. If you have any information please call the CBI at 719-647-5999 or to remain anonymous contact Pueblo Crime Stoppers at 719-542-STOP or www.pueblocrimestoppers.comThere is a large reward for Kelsie's return or location.
